    <p><span>AMEDAMA, Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024, etc.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Disney Music Parade: Encore [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/disney-music-parade-encore">Disney Music Parade: Encore</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch [16,315 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and the physical edition of <em><a title="Games > Marvel vs. Capcom Fighting Collection: Arcade Classics [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics">Marvel vs. Capcom Fighting Collection: Arcade Classics</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,441 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a> and Switch are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-928051"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are the <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,379 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,372 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and Switch versions of <em><a title="Games > AMEDAMA [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/amedama">AMEDAMA</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024 [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/microsoft-flight-simulator-2024">Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024</a></em> for Xbox Series and <a title="Platforms > PC [21,717 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, <em><a title="Games > HIGHSPEED Etoile Paddock Stories [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/highspeed-etoile-paddock-stories">HIGHSPEED Etoile Paddock Stories</a></em> for Switch, and more.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through Play-Asia links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU24</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em>AMEDAMA</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/amedama-multi-language/13/70hkbf?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>) – Launching digitally worldwide.</li><li><em>Disney Music Parade: Encore</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/disney-music-parade-encore/13/70hmgr?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li><em>HIGHSPEED Etoile Paddock Stories</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/highspeed-etoile-paddock-stories/13/70hdgp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)<ul><li>Limited Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/highspeed-etoile-paddock-stories-limited-edition/13/70hdgx?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
        </li><li><em>Marvel vs. Capcom Fighting Collection: Arcade Classics</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics-multi-langu/13/70hczl?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS4</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics-multi-langu/13/70hd0j?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>) – Launching worldwide.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics/13/70hd2z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS4</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics/13/70hd33?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics/13/70hd37?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS4</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics-code-in-a-b/13/70hd3b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>Asian Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics-multi-langu/13/70hd0n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS4</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/marvel-vs-capcom-fighting-collection-arcade-classics-multi-langu/13/70hd0p?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em>Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/microsoft-flight-simulator-2024-premium-deluxe-edition/13/70hshp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Series</a>) – Launching worldwide.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/microsoft-flight-simulator-2024-premium-deluxe-code-in-a-box/13/70hltd?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Series</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/microsoft-flight-simul